Statster
=======================

Tired of waiting 24 hours for your Google Analytics stats?
Want an API for your stats? Want total control?

* Filters out bots
* Lightweight and very fast
* REST API

Prerequisites
=============
* Merb

Getting started
===============
Check out the config file - should be pretty self explanatory. 

Add a call to the JavaScript stat.js (it will be generated the first time it's called), like this:
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://stat.example.com/stats.js"></script>

